        <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545">
            <head altrender="organization" id="a2">ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
            <p>Founded in 1949, the New York State Foundation cultivates, secures, and stewards
                financial resources to support the Cornell Cooperative Extension New York State 4-H
                program in developing and delivering 4-H youth development programs.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
            <p>Minutes of the Board of Directors and various other committee meetings, memos,
                financials, scholarship and trustee files.</p>
        </scopecontent>
